io.realm.dynamic

Class DynamicRealmObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.realm.RealmObject
      • io.realm.dynamic.DynamicRealmObject

  • public class DynamicRealmObject
extends RealmObject
    Class that wraps a normal RealmObject in order to allow dynamic access instead of a typed interface. Using a DynamicRealmObject is slower than using the regular model class.
